						               													<description>Pro Cycling The Board Game is 2020&amp;rsquo;s latest cycling board game, a fun and tactical game from the world of pro series. In the game you have to control a professional cycling team and get the most points by the end of the game. The following game items are available for this.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;1.    Team organization: From the five-person frame, assemble a four-person team according to the conditions of the race track &amp;ndash; for the flat sections SPRINTER, for the mountain sections CLIMBER, and a LEADER who leads the team.&amp;#10;2.    PELOTON: The field that is uniquely part of the competition.&amp;#10;3.    Track knowledge: Mapping the race track and getting to know the most important action points.&amp;#10;-    The colorful lines on both sides of the racing track indicate the difficulty level of the&amp;#10;    road and the level of steepness.&amp;#10;-    PART SPRINT: You can also earn valuable points during the race.&amp;#10;-    REFRESHING POINT: Additional action cards can be drawn.&amp;#10;-    BIG FALL, TECHNICAL ERROR: Various disadvantages can be obtained.&amp;#10;4.    Game dice and action die: The player makes the moves using the two dice.&amp;#10;5.    Action Cards: Action cards can be used to launch actions.&amp;#10;-    BREAKAWAY CARD: This card can be used to break away from the peloton.&amp;#10;-    ATTACK CARD: It gives the player an opportunity for a quick attack.&amp;#10;-    PELOTON CARD: Used to increase the pace of the field.&amp;#10;6.    In addition to action cards, other special actions can be used, such as a sprint, helping each other, helping the leader.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The board game is not only for bike fans, but also offers fun for the whole family. The number of players: 2-4 people. The duration of a game is 40-60 minutes depending on the number of players. The rulebook is available in the following languages: Hungarian, English, German, French, Italian, Spanish.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
